<h1 style="color:#0099FF">OT scheduling and management</h1>

<p><b>Operating Room Management </b>is a complex task where numerous resources must come together in order to achieve 
efficiency. Surgeon availability, operating team scheduling, patient related information, equipment, and support must all 
be carefully orchestrated.</p>
<p>DRMHOPE <b> Operating Theater Scheduling and operation management in hospital</b> is a web based software application
 that provides clinicians and administrators with all the available information on each surgical procedure planned,
  underway, or completed. It includes features like operation management in hospital, <b>operating theater management,</b>
  operating theater scheduling, pre-admission consultations, documentation of operating. It also includes clinical notes for 
  procedures, sterilization management and transcription. It also includes clinical notes for procedures, sterilization
   management and transcription.</p>


<h2>Benefits</h2>
<ul>
<li>	Ensure optimal utilization of OR theatres and time available in the OR</li>
<li>	Optimize the utilization of resources for better capacity planning</li>
<li>	Enable material requirements planning according to the schedule and plan</li>
<li>	Provide detailed costing for each procedure</li>
<li>	Improves personnel availability</li>
<li>	Allows efficient follow-up on all operating room activities</li>
<li>	Decrease patient delays</li>
<li>	Increases patient safety</li>
</ul>

